# --- Gold-set intermediates (Layer 3, D-024/D-025): large or regenerable slices.
# The MERGED data/gold/gold.jsonl is the durable committed artifact (real + synthetic).
data/gold/candidates.jsonl
data/gold/review.md
data/gold/gold_forum.jsonl
data/gold/gold_synth.jsonl

# --- RAGAS eval datasets (Layer 5d): contain the forum accepted-answer body as `reference`,
# which D-019 says never to commit. The ragas_*.json SCORES (numbers only) ARE committed;
# regenerate a dataset from the gold set with ./tasks.ps1 ragas. ---
results/ragas_dataset_*.jsonl

